history.content:
Hi everyone! 👋

From April 24-26th, Cal Hacks at UC Berkeley and Postman are coming together to launch hack:now, a global open-to-all online hackathon giving students & professionals the opportunity to tackle immediate challenges posed by COVID-19. Y Combinator will also be partnering with this event to give one winning team the opportunity to interview for their Summer 2020 Batch.

🚀 Register to hack: https://hacknow.calhacks.io/
💻 Become a mentor: https://hacknow.calhacks.io/mentor/
🌟 Help us judge: https://hacknow.calhacks.io/judge/

If you have any questions or concerns, feel free to reach out to team@calhacks.io!
We hope to see you all soon!

Cheers,
The Cal Hacks Team
